Database:
Database is collection of data in a format that can be easily accessed (Digital)

Software application used to manage our Database is called DBMS(Data Base Managment System)

Types of Database
Relational                                 Non-Relational (NOSQL)
*Data stored in tables                     *Data not stored in tables
using : MYSQL                               using : mongoDB

what is  SQL?
Structure Query Language
It is a programming language used to interact with relational database.

It used from CRUD operations:
Create - To create database,tables,insert tuples in tables.
Read - To read data presnet in the databse.
Update - Modify already inserted data.
Delete - Delete databse,table or specfic data point/tuple/roe or multiple rows
